{"word":"G847 - αὐτοῦ - autoû - ow-too' - Here","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">αὐτοῦ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">autoû</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ow-too'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Here</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அங்கு"},{"paragraph":"in that place, there, here"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Genitive (that is, possessive) of <a href=\"#/G846 - αὐτός - autós - ow-tos'/846\">G846</a>, used as an adverb of location; properly belonging to the <i>same</i> spot, that is, <i>in this</i> (or <i>that</i>) <i>place:</i> - (t-) here.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}